3184
01:36:45,480 --> 01:36:46,120
Fortunately,

3185
01:36:46,120 --> 01:36:47,120
not long after I arrived,

3186
01:36:47,120 --> 01:36:49,400
I met my current wife.

3187
01:36:49,400 --> 01:36:50,480
After we got married,

3188
01:36:50,480 --> 01:36:51,800
and started a family,

3189
01:36:51,800 --> 01:36:53,960
I wanted to find

3190
01:36:53,960 --> 01:36:55,520
a relatively stable job.

3191
01:36:55,520 --> 01:36:57,960
With the money we could scrape together
at the time,

3192
01:36:57,960 --> 01:36:59,120
it was impossible

3193
01:36:59,120 --> 01:37:00,760
to open a restaurant.

3194
01:37:00,760 --> 01:37:03,680
So I opened a fish and chips shop.

3195
01:37:03,680 --> 01:37:04,520
A snack shop.

3196
01:37:04,520 --> 01:37:06,280
Yes, the cost was relatively low.

3197
01:37:06,760 --> 01:37:09,880
In New Zealand, fish and chips is like

3198
01:37:09,880 --> 01:37:11,760
Lanzhou pulled noodles back in China.

3199
01:37:11,760 --> 01:37:12,800
It's very popular.

3200
