3204
01:37:21,560 --> 01:37:23,520
Yes, the best in all of Rotorua.

3205
01:37:24,040 --> 01:37:24,720
Rotorua.

3206
01:37:25,680 --> 01:37:27,120
As an old overseas Chinese deeply rooted

3207
01:37:27,120 --> 01:37:28,000
in Rotorua

3208
01:37:28,000 --> 01:37:30,040
