over these decades.

3211
01:37:36,320 --> 01:37:38,040
The motherland
is getting stronger and stronger.

3212
01:37:38,040 --> 01:37:38,920
Now,

3213
01:37:38,920 --> 01:37:41,080
especially in the last
eight to ten years,

3214
01:37:41,080 --> 01:37:42,600
