3215
01:37:42,600 --> 01:37:44,520
Our Chinese people
still have a Chinese palate.

3216
01:37:44,520 --> 01:37:47,320
We love eating our Chinese food.

3217
01:37:47,320 --> 01:37:49,840
So my team and I

3218
01:37:49,840 --> 01:37:50,840
developed some

3219
01:37:50,840 --> 01:37:54,600
