3227
01:38:14,360 --> 01:38:15,880
Thank you.

3228
01:38:15,880 --> 01:38:17,280
Okay, thank you.

3229
01:38:21,280 --> 01:38:23,000
Today, through the backpacker

3230
01:38:23,000 --> 01:38:25,040
and self-drive travel,

3231
01:38:25,040 --> 01:38:27,680
