3241
01:38:42,920 --> 01:38:44,080
there are people relying

3242
01:38:44,080 --> 01:38:45,320
on perseverance and hard work

3243
01:38:45,560 --> 01:38:47,160
to live a passionate life.

3244
01:38:47,400 --> 01:38:49,800
Tomorrow, we'll continue to explore

3245
01:38:49,800 --> 01:38:51,920
more new things
in the Southern Hemisphere.

3246
01:38:52,320 --> 01:38:53,120
Thank you.

3247
01:38:53,120 --> 01:38:54,520
Thank you.

