01:42:17,680 --> 01:42:19,320
(Special Extra Episode Preview)
One person from the performance group

3358
01:42:19,320 --> 01:42:21,720
is controlled
by the observation group's commands.

3359
01:42:21,720 --> 01:42:22,880
Can we designate the other side

3360
01:42:22,880 --> 01:42:24,200
to decide who wears the headphones?

3361
01:42:24,200 --> 01:42:25,600
- Just hearing the voice?
- They designate it themselves.

3362
01:42:25,600 --> 01:42:26,960
If you designate it,

3363
01:42:26,960 --> 01:42:29,040
what's there to guess?

3364
01:42:29,040 --> 01:42:30,200
What are you playing?

3365
01:42:30,200 --> 01:42:31,400
I don't want to be on his team anymore.

3366
01:42:31,400 --> 01:42:33,040
I'm afraid of being controlled by Fei.

3367
01:42:33,472 --> 01:42:33,920
(Scary to think about)

3368
01:42:33,920 --> 01:42:35,160
No, our commands

3369
01:42:35,160 --> 01:42:36,880
can't be that dirty, right?

3370
01:42:37,120 --> 01:42:38,280
Only dirtier.

3371
01:42:38,400 --> 01:42:39,920
You'll see how dirty it gets later.

3372
01:42:46,040 --> 01:42:46,520
This...

3373
01:42:46,520 --> 01:42:48,240
This is weird.

3374
01:42:53,000 --> 01:42:54,080
Kiss Guo Jingfei.

3375
01:42:54,080 --> 01:42:54,360
Quick.

3376
01:42:54,520 --> 01:42:55,480
Don't you all know

3377
01:42:55,480 --> 01:42:56,240
that when I was young,

3378
01:42:56,240 --> 01:42:57,280
I was somewhat good-looking?

3379
01:42:59,720 --> 01:43:01,480
Get even more hyped for me!

3380
01:43:01,480 --> 01:43:03,600
A song that rocks this world!

3381
01:43:03,600 --> 01:43:04,920
So happy!

3382
01:43:05,280 --> 01:43:06,680
I'm 46 years old this year.

3383
01:43:06,680 --> 01:43:08,256
(Feel drained)

3384
01:43:08,360 --> 01:43:10,080
At first, I thought it was Naiwen.

3385
01:43:10,080 --> 01:43:11,240
At first, I thought it was

3386
01:43:11,240 --> 01:43:11,840
Yuwen.

3387
01:43:11,840 --> 01:43:13,640
Each of them
has very suspicious behavior.

3388
01:43:13,640 --> 01:43:15,720
Look at Cool Lei's desperate face.

3389
01:43:15,720 --> 01:43:16,560
I think it's him.

3390
01:43:16,817 --> 01:43:19,040
(Who is the one being controlled
by the commands?)
